to win an all-expense-paid trip to Europe and a feature in National Geographic magazine. Coming in Bordeaux Red, Aqua Blue and Midnight Black, the Camon 12 Series is powered by MediaTek’s helio P22 chipset that makes possible smart AI imaging, AI Camera, reliable connectivity and power efficiency and won’t get hot while performing powerful functions. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .